<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Ka Thagau En In</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka tha, va chieh inla, Jerusalem dai ah,
 Kalvari muol leh, thing leh than leh thisan va en in;
 Ziechun um zing inla, mipi chieh dawk mahleu,
 Lal phasak phat a luong lak thak;
 Than hawm chanin enin.

[V2]
 A na ka sa taluoi! ka hehpih Hukdampa
 Thisan loa hukdam thei hileh chu aw. Ka Lalpa
 Van khuo nguiin Saron tuoilo ding hiven
 Mahleh Isu, Nang din van pi a chim.

[V3]
 2. Aw ka Lalpa deihtak, Na Lalchutphah enin,
 Kei din thuoka mi than awnga van Lal cha na kuol chu;
 Ana ka sa taluoi! Ana ka sa taluoi!
 Bang ka lawh ta mai die leh aw.
 Than suong a khak zo tau.

[V4]
 3. Vakvai ding ka him,Lalpa khawia um na him?
 Kalvari tang chunga thi a Na mel ka muh lai kha;
 Tuhin ka lung a dawngka lungkham a khawk diek,
 Ka lunggil ah a cham.

[V5]
 4. Ka man thisan a hi, van Lal a ka hi ie,
 Khawvel sum leh sana loa thisan a tat ka hi;
 Ka pa In lam ka hei, buoina mei khel gamah,
 Zion tang ka gamah.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>50</hymn_number>
<author>Patea</author>
</song>